name: Headbands - Vintage Collection
description: Pearls, lace, tulle, diamantes, and delicate yarns... Vintage is all about beauty and timeless glamour. Each of these pieces is handcrafted to perfection using only the finest materials, so that your little princess can shine like the stars each piece is named after.

These ones have 2 baby facewashers in each one, but you can have baby socks or onesies instead, or tell me your theme... The possibilities are endless! Contact me with your requirements for a quote ♥ (When bought individually: $4 each).
